#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimer; is an application that lets you start an application after a "
"certain amount of time has passed."
msgstr ""
"&ktimer; je aplikacija, ki omogoča zagon aplikacije po preteku določenega "
"časa."

